            <title>[DATAMONGO-232] mongodb allow to $inc many fields in one query, but Updat().inc(firs).inc(last)  do only last inc </title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/DATAMONGO-232</link>
                <project id="10701" key="DATAMONGO">Spring Data MongoDB</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Mongodb allow to inc many fields in one query.&lt;br/&gt;
Update update = new Update().inc(&quot;counter&quot;, 1).inc(&quot;hourly.0&quot;, 1);&lt;br/&gt;
do (shell equivalent):&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;db.visitStat.update(&lt;/p&gt;
{shopId:1}
&lt;p&gt;, {$inc:{&apos;hourly.0&apos;:1}})&lt;br/&gt;
instead of (shell equivalent):&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;db.visitStat.update(&lt;/p&gt;
{shopId:1}
&lt;p&gt;, {$inc:{&apos;hourly.0&apos;:1,counter:1}})&lt;/p&gt;



&lt;p&gt;shell example:&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;gt; db.visitStat.find()&lt;/p&gt;
{ &quot;_id&quot; : ObjectId(&quot;4e3703dd2249c6b5237e6096&quot;), &quot;counter&quot; : 4, &quot;day&quot; : 1, &quot;hourly&quot; : [

], &quot;month&quot; : 7, &quot;shopId&quot; : 1, &quot;widgetId&quot; : 1, &quot;year&quot; : 2011 }
